# M6 m6-pickup-placement — visual proof that concourse's right-
# doorway AMMO_SECONDARY (mirror of the left-doorway pickup at col
# 23) now lands at col 76 — atrium-side of the right wing-side
# cover stub at col 77. Pre-fix the mirror x of W-23 = 77 placed
# the pickup INSIDE the stub.

window 1280 720
out build/shots/m6_placement_concourse
seed 1 2

map concourse

# Spawn just east of the right doorway stub so the camera frames
# both stub and pickup. Right stub: col 77 rows 52..55. Pickup is
# now at col 76 row 55.
spawn_at 2530 1736

contact_sheet placement_concourse cols 2 cell 640 360

at 1  shot t1_doorway
at 60 shot t60_settled
at 90 end
